description:
This is a 10 minute workout called 'Quick Sprint Session! | 10 Minute Indoor Cycling Workout' from the channel GCN Training.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor biking and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
You'll need Exercise Bike for this workout.
The workout has a The Firestarter and The Speed & Power Sprint vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate and Challenging.

Original workout description: Only have 10 minutes to train, or need to warm up for a big effort? Manon is here with a quick progressive sprint session to get you firing on all cylinders!
